SPOINK bounces around on its tail.
The shock of its bouncing makes its
heart pump. As a result, this POKMON cannot afford to stop bouncing - if it
stops, its heart will stop.

SPOINK keeps a pearl on top of its head.
The pearl functions to amplify this
POKMONs psychokinetic powers. It is therefore on a constant search
for a bigger pearl.
